code: @Test public void defaultConfiguration() {     MappingWebEndpointPathMapper mapper = new MappingWebEndpointPathMapper(Collections.emptyMap()).     assertThat(PathMapper.getRootPath(Collections.singletonList(mapper), EndpointId.of("test"))).isEqualTo("test"). }

@Test public void userConfiguration() {     MappingWebEndpointPathMapper mapper = new MappingWebEndpointPathMapper(Collections.singletonMap("test", "custom")).     assertThat(PathMapper.getRootPath(Collections.singletonList(mapper), EndpointId.of("test"))).isEqualTo("custom"). }

@Test public void mixedCaseDefaultConfiguration() {     MappingWebEndpointPathMapper mapper = new MappingWebEndpointPathMapper(Collections.emptyMap()).     assertThat(PathMapper.getRootPath(Collections.singletonList(mapper), EndpointId.of("testEndpoint"))).isEqualTo("testEndpoint"). }

@Test public void mixedCaseUserConfiguration() {     MappingWebEndpointPathMapper mapper = new MappingWebEndpointPathMapper(Collections.singletonMap("test-endpoint", "custom")).     assertThat(PathMapper.getRootPath(Collections.singletonList(mapper), EndpointId.of("testEndpoint"))).isEqualTo("custom"). }
